data.description: Make this a holiday present for yourself. This single family four-bedroom home located in Temple is just what your family and you have been waiting for. Enjoy both the spacious front and backyard and never worry about parking as this home boasts a long driveway which features plenty of parking and a garage. Upon entering the living room, you will have the perfect view of the playground which sits catty-corner from your new home and is just a few short blocks from the school. Stain the original hardwood floors in the living room or place a nice plush throw rug down and begin to decorate your new living quarters. Enter the eat-in kitchen which features new floors, beautiful backsplash and an apron sink. The home will include both the refrigerator and the stove. Located on the first floor you will also find two bedrooms, one of which the previous owner had as the primary. On the second floor, you will find two additional bedrooms with all new flooring. There are so many possibilities within this home, you could make the second floor your primary suite and have your own privacy. While you are planning where your furniture will go, don’t forget to check out the full bath which has also been updated. Laundry is located in the basement and the Seller is leaving both the washer and dryer.    The Seller’s Disclosure will be uploaded soon. However, while this property is in good shape, the Seller is selling it As-Is.
